the nice thing to have qt-creator installed is that, when you navigate to a .ui file and double click it, it will be opened with qtdesigner

### Alt-G Alt-D show diff
### doc
move cursor to the class or object, and press F1, then you get the
doc, nice

### debugger
it just use gdb

### shortcut

right click in a opened source file, and you will get very useful shortcuts
